  <brief_title>The Effect of Angiotensin II Type 1 Receptor Antagonists on the Size and Expansion Rate of Abdominal Aortas in Hypertensive Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>the Effect of Angiotensin II Type 1 Receptor Antagonists on the Size and Expansion Rate of Abdominal Aortas in Hypertensive Patients</official_title>
